### 用户 API 测试

### 列出所有用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Accept: application/json

### 获取单个用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

### 创建用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "newuser",
    "password": "123456",
    "email": "newuser@example.com",
    "status": 1
}

### 更新用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/update/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "updateduser",
    "email": "updated@example.com",
    "status": 1
}

### 删除用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/delete/3
Accept: application/json

### 文章 API 测试

### 列出所有文章
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Accept: application/json

### 获取单个文章
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/1
Accept: application/json

### 创建文章
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "New Article",
    "content": "This is a new article content.",
    "user_id": 1,
    "status": 1
}

### 更新文章
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles/update/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Updated Article",
    "content": "This is the updated content.",
    "status": 1
}

### 删除文章
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/delete/5
Accept: application/json

### 高级查询示例

### 按用户名模糊搜索
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users?username_like=user
Accept: application/json

### 按状态过滤
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users?status=1
Accept: application/json

### 按创建时间范围查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users?created_at_gte=2024-01-01&created_at_lt=2024-12-31
Accept: application/json

### 分页查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 排序
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users?orderBy=-created_at,username
Accept: application/json

### 组合查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles?user_id=1&status=1&orderBy=-created_at&pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 使用 Save 更新用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "username": "updateduser",
    "email": "updated@example.com",
    "status": 1
} 